graph TD
    A[Patient Arrival] --> B{Registration}
    B -->|Records Dept| C[Capture NHIS Card Details]
    C --> D{Patient Type?}
    
    %% Outpatient Flow
    D -->|Outpatient| E[OPD Consultation]
    E --> F[Diagnosis: ICD-10 Code]
    F --> G[Procedures: G-DRG Codes]
    G --> H[Prescriptions: NHIS Med Codes]
    H --> I{Claim Trigger}
    I -->|After Visit| J[Generate Outpatient Claim]
    
    %% Inpatient Flow
    D -->|Inpatient| K[Admission]
    K --> L[Daily Services]
    L --> M[Diagnosis: ICD-10]
    M --> N[Procedures: G-DRG]
    N --> O[Medications: NHIS Codes]
    O --> P{Discharge?}
    P -->|Yes| Q[Generate Inpatient Claim]
    
    %% Common Flow
    J --> R[Claim Validation]
    Q --> R
    R --> S{Batch Ready?}
    S -->|Yes| T[Add to Monthly Batch]
    T --> U[Generate NHIA XML]
    U --> V[Submit to NHIA]